<lyrics>
[1]
 Saviour, like a shepherd lead us
 Much we need your tender care
 In your pleasant pastures feed us
 For our use your folds prepare
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 That you&apos;ve bought us - we are yours
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 That you&apos;ve bought us - we are yours
 
[2]
