 Be the guardian of our way
 Keep your flock, from sin defend us
 Seek us when we go astray
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 That you hear us when we pray
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 That you hear us when we pray
 
[3]
 You have promised to receive us
 Poor and sinful though we be
 You have mercy to relieve us
 Grace to cleanse and pow&apos;r to free
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 You sustain our lives each day
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 You sustain our lives each day
 
[4]
 We would always seek your favour
 We would always do your will
 Blessed Lord and only Saviour
 With your love our spirits fill
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 For your love that never fails
 Lord, we praise you [2x]
 For your love that never fails
 
